                                                                                                        <div class="gem-tta-panel-heading">
                                                                                                            <h4 class="gem-tta-panel-title gem-tta-controls-icon-position-left"> <a href="#section-25678b3-5" data-vc-accordion data-vc-container=".gem-tta-container"> <span class="gem-tta-title-text"> Why should you consider Salesforce CPQ and quote-to-cash Solutions? </span> <span class="gem-tta-controls-icon gem-tta-controls-icon-opened"> <i aria-hidden="true" class="fas fa-minus"></i> </span> <span class="gem-tta-controls-icon gem-tta-controls-icon-closed"> <i aria-hidden="true" class="fas fa-plus"></i> </span> </a></h4>
                                                                                                        </div>
                                                                                                        <div class="gem-tta-panel-body">
                                                                                                            <div class="gem-text-output">
                                                                                                                <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Salesforce Quote-to-Cash is a complete CPQ solution. Automated tools help you generate accurate quotes, error-free contracts, and professional proposals easily and quickly. </span></p>
                                                                                                                <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Streamlined billing and revenue recognition help you collect payments, manage subscriptions, and account for revenue received. Perhaps best of all, the entire tool is accessible through a single dashboard, so that you can understand and guide your sales process from a unified central location.Salesforce Quote-to-Cash is a scalable, cloud-based, universally compatible tool to help keep your leads on the right track.</span></p>
